                    "description": "Renewi Organics is market leader in organic waste processing. This new businessline of Renewi was created after the acquisition of Rotie Organics in Amsterdam by Orgaworld earlier this year and more recently the merger with Semler in Son. Three leading companies and known brands in the Dutch market, working from six locations.\n\nWe now created a nationwide collection infractructure for overdate materials & swill and three depackaging facilities efficiently scattered throughout the country. With our existing four processing facilities for organic waste  from households (SSO) and sludges we turn organic waste into valuable and circular products. \n\nBesides efficient operations we also walk ahead with our Lelystad Innovation Center. Together with several partners we facilitate knowledge development on the products & processes of the future. With this portfolio we have a unique proposition for all types of customers and we are proud to serve many of them.",
